---
title: Coconut Lentil, Prawn & Green Bean Dhal with Yoghurt & Chilli Flatbreads
description: Dhal is always wholesome and delicious but this version raises the bar, with a creamy coconut base, mild spices and multiple veggies to keep things interesting. Plus, you'll quickly become addicted to the chilli flatbreads for dipping – they're easy to create and make this meal extraordinary!
